SUMMARY:Poetry Group of Evanston Writers Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Evanston Writers Workshop\nThe Evanston Writers Workshop Poetry Group will be meeting on the second Thursday of the month\, from 7-9 P.M\, at Sketchbook Brewery in Evanston.\n\nPeople may submit 1-2 poems per person for critique via our submission form at the following url:\nhttps://form.jotform.com/251125391424147\n\nTo find the poems we'll be reviewing for this month's meeting\, visit our group website\, https://evanstonwritersworkshop.org/ and look for the link to our submissions file drive under "Calendar and Submissions". The submitted poems will be accessible the week of the event.
