SUMMARY:Sketchbook Evanston Open Mic Night
DESCRIPTION:Evanston Writers Workshop\nSketchbook Brewing Co. in Evanston is hosting an open mic night the last Monday of every month\, open to all. Come grab a drink and enjoy the talents of other local musicians\, writers\, and creatives\, and maybe even sign up to read some of your own work.\n\nSign-up starts at 6pm\, and the open-mic starts at 6:30pm.\n\nPlease note this open mic is run and hosted by Sketchbook\, and open to the general public. This invite is for Evanston Writers Workshop members interested in attending the event together.
